  <brief_title>Adiponectin and Insulin Resistance in Diabetic Nephropathy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Adiponectin is Positively Associated With Insulin Resistance in Subjects With Type 2 Diabetic Nephropathy and Effects by Angiotensin Type 1 Receptor Blocker Losartan</official_title>
  <sponsors>
