  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Plasma adiponectin concentration is inversely associated with renal function. There is little
      literature on adiponectin levels and regulation by antihypertensive medication with an
      angiotensin II-receptor blocker (ARB), especially in subjects with type 2 diabetes in
      different stage of chronic kidney disease (CKD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
